name: Parking Jeep Frenzy Reloaded - Real Driving Mania
name_original: Parking Jeep Frenzy Reloaded - Real Driving Mania
description:
Frenzy Parking Reloaded Jeep is an awesome parking game. Get ready to drive like a real jeep driver, face different missions and beat your own record. In this latest jeep driving and parking mission, you have to hit the main store, you get to try and test your skills on how good you can park a big semi truck! If you enjoy car parking and driving games.

Try this new SUV and 4 wheeler drive car for free. You have to drive fast because time is running fast and there are too many hurdles to avoid off. This is a real driving test for you. In some areas, you have to reverse your var in order to complete mission.

Features:

- Use steering to move sideways
- Press race button to accelerate.
- Press break to slow down speed.
- 3 different stages
- Total 30 levels
- Maximum smooth controls.
